{"tid":384022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞「破壞王」鐵通毀倒後鏡 長沙灣9車遭殃","createTime":"2017-09-02T03:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T16:09:29.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a102d17a50772747863391e60d1991e5921457b","tid":384022,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"長沙灣昌華街共9輛車的倒後鏡，凌晨懷疑被一名南亞裔男子以鐵通毀壞。警方正調查事件，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n現場為長沙灣昌華街41號對開，一名女子發現她停泊在上址的輕型貨車，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>懷疑被一名南亞裔男子以類似鐵通的硬物毀壞，於是報案。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，發現上址有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4輛私家車、4輛輕型貨車及1輛的士的倒後鏡被打破。</strong></span>經初步調查，案件列作刑事毀壞，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進，正追緝一名年約30至40歲，肥身材的非華裔男子，案發時身穿白色上衣及短褲。"},{"pid":"d506e85925c03b5bc2cf73aec93a2c1c8400966c","tid":384022,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"摘鳩佢器官啦屌"},{"pid":"e27b5cb23b8ca00f247d4e39041594389cb2a3af","tid":384022,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfa92fb368f94b2d722c02397749db9ba0090753","tid":384022,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪蝻亞啡皮差狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c4ab13b72d32dcf4e4f0329ce934e9d380853b","tid":384022,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"嗰頭好似唔算多蝻..."},{"pid":"a7a31aba94054cf883529bcd974f86130a6b43bd","tid":384022,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰頭好似唔算多蝻...</blockquote><br />\n錯！我本身向昌華街租左屋有十七年，係唔知點解近呢半年多撚左好多蝻，多數捕向大中華對出十字路，又或者成班向七仔門口對出打戥。"},{"pid":"a196abfd118efa948303fe26df78ba4b65aae7b3","tid":384022,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰頭好似唔算多蝻...</blockquote><br />\n錯！我本身向昌華街租左屋有十七年，係唔知點解近呢半年多撚左好多蝻，多數捕向大中華對出十字路，又或者成班向七仔門口對出打戥。</blockquote><br />\n唔係嘛<br />\n蝻真係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}